data.description: This Spacious home with NO CDD fees also has PAID OFF Solar panels! This large 4 bedroom & 3 and a half bathroom, home has Room for the whole family! Convenient commute to NAS. Located in the community of Forest Hammock in desirable Oakleaf Plantation. Enter into a large foyer through to an office with French doors. Open floor plan with shared living room and dining areas, great to entertain. The kitchen features 42'' cabinets with stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops, walk-in pantry, and a huge island with pendant lights above. All the bedrooms and laundry room are located upstairs. One bedroom has its own full bathroom. The primary bedroom features a double tray ceiling.
